headline.main: Christina McHale Will Meet Serena Williams at Miami Open

snippet: Christina McHale of the United States beat Misaki Doi, 6-2, 4-6, 7-5, at the Miami Open to set up a second-round showdown with Serena Williams.
lead_paragraph: Christina McHale of the United States beat Misaki Doi, 6-2, 4-6, 7-5, at the Miami Open to set up a second-round showdown with Serena Williams.
